OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,FLabour MP Tom Hayes criticises Nigel
OL,7,FFarage's remarks on the Henry Nowak
OL,8,Fcase as Reform UK's Cllr Linden
OL,9,FKemkaran defends her party leader on
OL,10,FITV's The Last Word
OL,12,FA Reform UK council leader has
OL,13,Fdefended Nigel Farage, after criticism
OL,14,Fof his call for people to respond to
OL,15,FHenry Nowak's death with "pure cold
OL,16,Frage".
OL,18,FThe party leader made the comments in
OL,19,Fa livestream on Tuesday morning, hours
OL,20,Fbefore scenes of disorder and violence
OL,21,Fon the streets of Southampton.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@EO]
