OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780672278
OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,FAsked on ITV's The Last Word whether
OL,7,FMr Farage had fanned the flames of
OL,8,Fdivision, Kent County Council leader
OL,9,FLinden Kenkaran said "I felt cold rage
OL,10,Fwatching that (bodycam) video and I'm
OL,11,Fsure millions of other people did in
OL,12,Fthis country".
OL,14,FHenry Nowak's killer, 23-year-old
OL,15,FVickrum Digwa, lied to Hampshire
OL,16,FPolice officers, claiming he had been
OL,17,Fthe victim of a racist attack on 3
OL,18,FDecember 2025.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@OpmrD@WpntD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
