OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780672278
OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,FBodycam video showed officers
OL,7,Fhandcuffing the 18-year-old student
OL,8,Fshortly before he died in Southampton,
OL,9,Fdespite him telling them he had been
OL,10,Fstabbed.
OL,12,FLabour's Tom Hayes told ITV Meridian's
OL,13,Fmonthly political programme: "You can
OL,14,Ffeel anger but what Nigel Farage was
OL,15,Fcalling for was for people to respond
OL,16,Fwith pure cold rage.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780672278
OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"I felt angry watching that bodycam
OL,7,Ffootage but I also have a
OL,8,Fresponsibility as an elected
OL,9,Fpolitician to channel that anger into
OL,10,Fsomething that makes things better."
OL,12,FIn the online live broadcast, streamed
OL,13,Fby Reform UK, Mr Farage paid tribute
OL,14,Fto the Nowak family, but then added:
OL,15,F"I suggest the rest of us respond to
OL,16,Fthis with pure cold rage."
OL,18,FEleven officers and a police dog were
OL,19,Finjured during clashes in Southampton
OL,20,Fon Tuesday evening.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]wD@AOUxD@ZO]
