OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,FWinchester MP, Danny Chambers, told
OL,7,FThe Last Word: "Nigel Farage had a
OL,8,Fchance to enact the wishes of Henry
OL,9,FNowak's father... who specifically
OL,10,Fcalled for this not to be a situation
OL,11,Fthat inflamed tension."
OL,13,FCllr Kemkaran responded that Mark
OL,14,FNowak "was speaking as a bereaved
OL,15,Fparent" whereas Nigel Farage was
OL,16,F"speaking as the leader of a political
OL,17,Fparty looking at systemic failures".
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@WO]vD@GOUwD@GO]xD@AOUyD@cO]
