OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780672278
OL,3,CLabour and Reform politicians dispute
OL,4,CNigel Farage's 'rage' over Henry Nowak
OL,6,FWhen asked if she would condemn the
OL,7,Fscenes of disorder, the KCC leader
OL,8,Freplied: "Of course, we all condemn
OL,9,Fthe violence. Nobody wants to see
OL,10,Friots on the streets."
OL,12,FThe Nowak family met Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fand Conservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,14,Fin Westminster this week.
OL,16,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC) said its independent
OL,18,Finvestigation "remains ongoing".
OL,26,@pD@JOUrD@VO]
